graph TD
    User([User / Browser]) -->|enters guess| App[app.py - Streamlit UI]
    App -->|reads difficulty| GetRange[get_range_for_difficulty]
    App -->|validates input| ParseGuess[parse_guess]
    ParseGuess -->|valid int| CheckGuess[check_guess]
    CheckGuess -->|outcome + message| App
    App -->|updates| SessionState[(st.session_state)]
    SessionState -->|secret, attempts, score, status, history| App
    App -->|outcome + attempt_number| UpdateScore[update_score]
    UpdateScore -->|new score| SessionState
    CheckGuess -->|Win| BalloonEffect[Balloons + Win Message]
    CheckGuess -->|Too High or Too Low| HintMessage[Hint Message Displayed]
    App -->|imports| LogicUtils[logic_utils.py]

    subgraph Core Logic
        GetRange
        ParseGuess
        CheckGuess
        UpdateScore
    end

    subgraph Streamlit State
        SessionState
    end

    subgraph UI Layer
        App
        BalloonEffect
        HintMessage
    end
